==English==

===Etymology===
from the name ''Angiospermae''

===Noun===
'''angiosperms'''
#(''botany'') The [[plant]] group characterized by having [[ovule]]s enclosed in an [[ovary]].  The scientific name varies with the [[taxonomic system]] being used: the ''[[Angiospermae]]'', ''[[Magnoliophyta]]'', ''[[Magnoliopsida]]'', etc.

===Synonym===
flowering plants

===Derived term===
* [[angiosperm]]